{"type": "article", "id": 37602, "title": "还记得索尼的磁带机和随身听吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-08T23:02:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 37463, "name": "The PARK-ING GINZA"}, {"id": 186, "name": "索尼"}, {"id": 37464, "name": "タンスのゲン"}, {"id": 37465, "name": "Hanna Dovhan"}, {"id": 37466, "name": "Mike Karolos"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 174, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170208221959iHmMFrqldzX6aOpk.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The PARK-ING GINZA X SONY by Hiroshi Fujiwara</h3><p>在已经落成 50 年的东京银座索尼大楼地下停车场，有一家由设计师藤原浩开设的概念店铺 The PARK-ING GINZA。为了让更多人感受到索尼公司经典产品的魅力，同时恰逢索尼大楼预计于 3 月拆除重建，藤原便与索尼联手打造了一系列实用的周边。各种规格的收纳包和坐垫披上了软盘、磁带机、Walkman 这些一度是索尼看板产品的外衣，目前正在索尼大楼地下停车场展出。由于还原度很高，它们看起来就像是货真价实的设备一样，充满了复古感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222043oRgwzlfcC1YUhvbx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222043JQ78pUMsZ6FtboH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222043Abzg4VW2hYmHK6TF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222044vifn0Au68gjMRSxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222043ZlLCA3djKVb5Dhaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222044cSqdJ2zRBQrtu3Ym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Buddy the Game Chair by Tansu no Gen</h3><p>玩主机游戏的时候是不是总觉得姿势别扭？最近来自电子游戏大国日本的家具公司<a href=\"http://www.tansu-gen.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">タンスのゲン</a>就专门设计了一款让人可以更舒服地玩游戏的座椅，还给它取了一个很有亲和力的名字 Buddy the Game Chair。以成为玩家的“好伙伴”为目标的 Buddy 有着和躺椅相似的造型，红、青、棕三种配色走的也是活泼年轻的路线。椅背的部分可以随意调节，玩游戏时就有地方撑着手肘了。它将于 4 月 28 日正式发售，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%82%BF%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%B2%E3%83%B3-%E3%82%B2%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E5%BA%A7%E6%A4%85%E5%AD%90-%E3%83%AA%E3%82%AF%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%8B%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0-%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A3%E3%83%89%E3%82%A6%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3-16210002/dp/B00GLPTLOO/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1485207169&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=%E3%82%BF%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%B2%E3%83%B3%E5%BA%A7%E6%A4%85%E5%AD%90\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>预定，售价为 4980 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222105zUebYqLW37u40orH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304348\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222105rSTcMiURHKjEXmFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222106makvYQT0clLErIuF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222105LyZIh8jBCxlHMGkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Little Monster Jar by Z-Inhouse</h3><p>谁说厨房不能走俏皮可爱的路线？这些来自<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>的小怪兽陶瓷储物罐各有一双尖耳朵罐盖，让你可以放心地将调味品或是其他小物交给它们保管。圆润的外型加上撞色搭配，无论放在哪里都能吸引到好奇的视线。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300089\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，单个售价 53 元，组合价为 152 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222124OhrkibFELCMNTWJ7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222124x2CAreKqOMDRpZHv.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222124FSadcB1bwIJP5xjR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702082221246AbtkIl7a4DWrGvR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Botanium</h3><p>对想在家种点小蔬果之类的但却没有时间和精力（以及空间）的人来说，水耕是一个不错的选择，我们之前也介绍过不少相关的产品。最近来自瑞典的设计团队则将功能和极简的外观结合在一起，研发了这款名为 Botanium 的水耕装置。和同类产品相比，长得像花瓶一样的 Botanium 有着小身材的优势。从示意图上看，它的内部结构是一套简洁明了且相当完备的系统，只要将水、肥料和培养液倒入容器再插上电源，它会自动控制植物的浇水时机和水量。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/158584247/botanium-grow-edible-greens-fast-and-effortlessly\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 539 瑞典克朗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222146eajBNUn91w8mQL3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222145Wk5zTjX0JSOfP9y7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222147S4UV8MsC2RuztH0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222146Gxwyd3nrLoVm7fzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702082221460gF15MXf8lTJnHKS.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222146Eyu59s3SjWIzrawH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.807353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Woolsculpture by Hanna Dovhan</h3><p>把食物拟人化并不是什么新奇的创意，不过由乌克兰设计师 Hanna Dovhan 制作的食物羊毛毡玩偶们或许称得上是食物拟人界里数一数二的抱抱爱好者了：有了毛绒绒的质感加持，当这些胖嘟嘟的鸡蛋和牛油果（努力地）拥抱在一起，真的是让人很不忍心再把它们拆散。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Wooolsculpture\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到目前在售的辣椒和蘑菇两款羊毛毡，售价分别为 35 和 45 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702082222160GqTkLRUXwz6nI7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222217kJw9dFLXbnyauABI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222216aAIt0jTe8g3PpX7c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222216m0e6yawlRYf98cQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.840000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702082222164MXtN0ked1RoOj6Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843860\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222217V6TWykoidBEI1qjz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Elo Soaps by Mike Karolos</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.elosoap.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elo</a> 是希腊一个以橄榄油为原料的手工皂品牌，为了让自己的产品能在游客经常光顾的礼品店内脱颖而出，他们委托现居雅典的英国平面设计师 <a href=\"http://smirapdesigns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mike Karolos</a> 创作一套以希腊神话故事中的神明为主题的包装。考虑到不少希腊礼品包装选择了相同的主题，Karolos 最后采用几何图形以波普艺术风重新呈现了诸如宙斯、波赛冬、雅典娜这些希腊众神的形象，看上去有一种彩绘玻璃的感觉。除了包含这些插画的标签卡片之外，肥皂本身仅通过白色包装纸和一根彩色的绳子包扎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222328VvhQbLBckCsjMdSG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222328o358dqrGUEpCMc4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222328kufXiHyDUB8h5RAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702082223283JwsEDYUbjoAc0yd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170208222328Yy7bD9U2GVF8IEJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.074667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}